name: Multifruit
description:
The first collector of this NFT will receive this original painting. 1st collector, please DM me via Twitter @Maks_Denysenko

Every new picture is a holiday for me, but when I write great works I feel like I have a birthday, but in fact this day is born living, breathing matter.
If you focus on the fragment that caught your attention, then after some deep breathing you will see how the image begins to move.

Artwork created by Maksym Denysenko in 2016, spray paint on canvas, 190x99 cm, 4243x2181 pix.
